definitions.definition: The act of attaining ; the act of arriving at or reaching ; the act of obtaining by exertion or effort .
examples: My attainment of proficiency in German was due to years upon years of study.

definitions.definition: That which is attained, or obtained by exertion.

main_definition: The act of attaining ; the act of arriving at or reaching ; the act of obtaining by exertion or effort .
